{"tid":154170,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"反了反了！梁振英成為香港特首兼中國領導人","createTime":"2017-03-13T06:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T06:10:28.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63e086dc99b1000225beb3a279573e977d7b5d22","tid":154170,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:04:46.000Z","msg":"全國政協十二屆五次會議閉幕會今早9時30分在人民大會堂舉行，會上以2066票贊成、13票反對、16票棄權、6人未按表決器，表決通過香港特首梁振英出任全國政協副主席。<br />\n<br />\n當表決結果公布後，梁振英隨即被請上主席台，他先向台上台下鞠躬，然後在第一排就座，躋身國家領導人行列。連同前特首董建華，本港現有兩人位居政協副主席，而梁振英亦成為第一位在任特首同時兼任<span style=\"color: red;\">國家領導人</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170313/s00001/1489369542190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170313%2Fs00001%2F1489369542190&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=0650bf06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170313%2Fs00001%2F1489369542190&h=228ea23e\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170313/s00001/1489369542190</a>"},{"pid":"6460e38a7e266b0622c43c3431be781e7dd25f30","tid":154170,"uid":10313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:07:03.000Z","msg":"有幾多個副主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77c55c2f32f27859d7cf6b92cf58e53bd0003b1","tid":154170,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:08:04.000Z","msg":"習總下緊一盤好大嘅棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ce4f82a88f299f470b06dae8c263c9a33d7f8c","tid":154170,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>習總下緊一盤好大嘅棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依加689先係中國領導人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9d6b77c77de5f639be86787a0c2217393fb0d0","tid":154170,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:10:28.000Z","msg":"政協副主席的確係國家領導人，不過係大陸一般同時會有80人擁有呢個稱號。"}]}